---
title: Swedish-Style Beyond Meat® Meatballs with Creamy Gravy and Buttery Snap Peas
description: Skip a trip to a certain Scandinavian shop and make these DIY Swedish Beyond Meat® meatballs at home! Soften seasoned breadcrumbs with a bit of milk for extra-tender results.

